---
import BaseLayout from "../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Affiliate Disclosure" lang="en">

<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-12">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
  <p class="text-[var(--text-muted)] mb-8">How we earn from recommendations.</p>
  <div class="space-y-4 text-sm text-[var(--text-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
    <div class="card p-6"><h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">What Are Affiliate Links?</h3><p>Affiliate links contain tracking codes. We may earn a commission when you register or purchase through them.</p></div>
    <div class="card p-6"><h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">Impact on You</h3><p>Using affiliate links does not increase your cost. In some cases, you may get additional benefits.</p></div>
    <div class="card p-6"><h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">Our Principle</h3><p>We only recommend tools and services we genuinely use and endorse.</p></div>
  </div>
</div>

</BaseLayout>
